# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
# WUZO â€” .htaccess para Hostinger
# Arquivo: public_html/wuzo.com.br/.htaccess
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

Options -MultiViews -Indexes

# â”€â”€ SPA â€” redireciona tudo para index.html â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
RewriteEngine On
RewriteBase /

# NÃ£o redireciona arquivos e pastas que existem
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d

# Tudo o mais vai para index.html
RewriteRule ^ index.html [QSA,L]

# â”€â”€ CORS â€” permite chamadas para app.wuzo.com.br â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
<IfModule mod_headers.c>
    # Permite o frontend chamar a API no subdomÃ­nio
    Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "https://app.wuzo.com.br"
    Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Methods "GET, POST, OPTIONS"
    Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Headers "Content-Type, Authorization"

    # SeguranÃ§a bÃ¡sica
    Header always set X-Content-Type-Options "nosniff"
    Header always set X-Frame-Options "SAMEORIGIN"
    Header always set Referrer-Policy "strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
</IfModule>

# â”€â”€ Cache de assets estÃ¡ticos â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
<IfModule mod_expires.c>
    ExpiresActive On
    <FilesMatch "\.(css|js|woff2|woff|ttf|svg|png|jpg|webp|ico)$">
        ExpiresDefault "access plus 30 days"
        Header set Cache-Control "max-age=2592000, public"
    </FilesMatch>
    # HTML nunca em cache (garante atualizaÃ§Ã£o imediata)
    <FilesMatch "\.html$">
        ExpiresDefault "access plus 0 seconds"
        Header set Cache-Control "no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate"
        Header set Pragma "no-cache"
    </FilesMatch>
</IfModule>

# â”€â”€ CompressÃ£o GZIP â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
<IfModule mod_deflate.c>
    AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE text/html text/css application/javascript
</IfModule>

# â”€â”€ ForÃ§a HTTPS â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
RewriteCond %{HTTPS} off
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301]
